<br>
No offense Tux, you did what you thought was fine.  And you can't be everywhere, you play a lot, but need time to yourself just as anyone does.  But if an officer was there onsite and this happened, Micro and Jora wouldnt be questioned if they did the right thing or not....the officer at hand would instead.<br>
